WEBVTT

00:15.531 --> 00:18.312
Shri Mataji: So now,

00:27.725 --> 00:31.812
we can start with the washing of the Hands.

00:32.013 --> 00:34.517
“Yā Devī sarva bhūteshu” you say

00:34.718 --> 00:38.805
and hundred and eight names of the Mother
after that.

00:39.006 --> 00:41.718
Guido: Yes, Shri Mataji.

00:47.968 --> 00:52.633
The Devas said, “Salutation to the Devi,
to the Mahadevi.

00:52.834 --> 00:57.649
Salutations always to Her who is ever
auspicious.

00:57.850 --> 01:04.179
Salutations to Her who is the primordial
cause of the sustaining power.

01:04.380 --> 01:08.789
With attention we have made obeisance
to Her.

01:08.990 --> 01:13.484
Salutations to Her who is terrible, to Her
who is eternal.

01:13.685 --> 01:17.922
Salutations to Gauri, the supporter
of the universe.

01:18.123 --> 01:20.820
Salutations only to Her

01:21.021 --> 01:27.735
who is of the form of the moon and
moonlight, and happiness itself.

01:27.936 --> 01:30.732
We bow to Her who is welfare.

01:30.933 --> 01:35.076
We make salutations to Her who is
prosperity and success.

01:35.277 --> 01:38.037
Salutation to the consort of Shiva,

01:38.238 --> 01:44.061
who is Herself the good fortune as well
as misfortune of kings.

01:44.262 --> 01:46.678
Salutations always to Durga.

01:46.896 --> 01:51.006
Shri Mataji: She is good Fortune for Her
children and misfortune for Her enemies.

01:51.207 --> 01:56.191
Sahaja Yogi: Bolo Jagan Mata
Shri Nirmala Devi Ki! All Yogis: Jai!

01:56.795 --> 02:01.990
Guido: Salutations always to Durga who
takes one across in difficulties,

02:02.191 --> 02:05.542
who is essence, who is the author
of everything,

02:05.743 --> 02:08.839
who is knowledge and discrimination,

02:09.040 --> 02:14.801
and who is blue black and also smoke
light in complexion.

02:15.002 --> 02:20.894
We prostrate before Her who is at once
most gentle and most terrible.

02:21.095 --> 02:24.402
We salute Her again and again.

02:24.603 --> 02:28.784
Salutations to Her who is the support
of all the world.

02:28.985 --> 02:34.684
Salutations to the Devi who is the form
of volition.

02:35.673 --> 02:37.815
Salutations again and again to the Devi

02:38.071 --> 02:43.372
